{"tid":1242341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！620、621想救義士嘅入黎！！！","createTime":"2019-06-19T04:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T07:25:02.000Z","uid":263778,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"28cd171cbf6a3c8afd6db41edc40731b6b337984","tid":1242341,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"想救義士嘅各位！！我地需要話比大衆聼我地救義士嘅訴求！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n620、621最大嘅問題係，宜家好多人已經因爲林鄭暫緩條例+道歉而<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">妥協</span></span>，唔想再出黎，尤其是好多<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中老</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非</span></span><br />\n之前200萬+1游行可以咁多人響應，係因爲有呢班中老同和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一旦失去左佢地，我地將會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勢孤力弱</span></span>！！！<br />\n所以宜家我地好需要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>文宣</strong></span></span>，教育大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">勇武嘅作用同重要性</span></strong></span><br />\n仲有，只要勇武派GG左，我地以後再發生類似送中條例呢類型嘅事，就會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無人出黎抗爭</span></span>！！！<br />\n有都無用，單係得和理非係唔夠威脅政府架！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多和理非真係好天真唔明，所以大家加大力度宣傳！！！<br />\n<br />\n另外，我認爲620、621嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">focus</span></strong>真係應該去返：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 撤銷暴動指控+無條件釋放義士<br />\n2. 追究警察濫用暴力</span></strong><br />\n其他嘅訴求請暫時先放埋一邊，因爲上面呢兩個擺耐左就真係無得追究返<br />\n而撤回修例嘅事，好多人都已經放棄左，就算再講都未必可以叫到人出黎<br />\n至於真普選我地等G20先，區議會選舉都可以慢慢黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>宜家務必集中猛推呢兩個訴求，先可以團結力量！！！如果唔係，訴求太散渙，大家只會覺得好迷失，或者以爲場仗已經打完！！！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc855103e815375db1c04188b8b1015990b351fc","tid":1242341,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"fb050d9df6e7e8541db5dd63eb7f0fd985b8cbc9","tid":1242341,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:30:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c23a5cc63d2edfbe6fcc13ad8b1351cc4c2bd770","tid":1242341,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:33:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"786a971f7c1982b324301a13427c4fa5b9407cbf","tid":1242341,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"77473c3a7fb0542788522efe4442721ba0503aae","tid":1242341,"uid":246118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dacc6e60f295d9ce26e24febcaf4006bd9e96922","tid":1242341,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df7337a2decd928b3b1fd86db6c564737525f830","tid":1242341,"uid":90743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6004c14a3cb1565f6cd2033ed4ae0708e44e4598","tid":1242341,"uid":8891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:35:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"108f25a294246e58e82e139db70c0ef2f93144e9","tid":1242341,"uid":8086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:35:27.000Z","msg":"好同意<br />\n但係如果樓主加返幾張文宣圖比大家傳會更好<br />\n如果唔係經常見到po話要文宣， 但又一張圖都見唔到，想share都唔知share乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad9c79581cb7393c587ea3cff2a7d3008e96f7c","tid":1242341,"uid":179984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:38:17.000Z","msg":"PUSH<b